<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito+Sans:400,400i,700,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #D9534F;
            font-family: "Nunito Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 42px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            color: #404F5E;
            font-family: "Nunito Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .icon-container {
            border-radius: 50%;
            height: 200px;
            width: 200px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #FDEDEC, #F8FAF5);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(217, 83, 79, 0.2);
        }

        .icon {
            font-size: 100px;
            color: #D9534F;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 120px auto;
            max-width: 500px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D9534F, #C9302C);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C9302C, #D9534F);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(217, 83, 79, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-container">
            <i class="icon">âœ—</i>
        </div>
        <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
        <p>Your payment could not be processed.<br> Please try again later or use a different payment method.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="/Orders">Retry Payment</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
